title: sagarbansal21
author: sagarbansal21
content: AdLunam, an upcoming crypto IDO launchpad, has announced a strategic partnership with Liquidex, a provider of crypto market-making services for token projects. This partnership is expected to bring higher liquidity, less risk of price manipulation, high trading volume, and better listing prices for the tokens launched on AdLunam’s platform.Learn more: https://medium.com/adlunam-inc/adlunam-joins-forces-with-liquidex-to-provide-high-liquidity-to-tokens-b8c303546e53
